No statement on cost allocation; Processor could charge premium fees for statutory cooperation.
Lacks requirement to certify deletion/return; no timeline specified.
Merely lists examples; Exhibit B blank; no minimum baseline or audit/report frequency.
Silent on Transfer Impact Assessments (TIAs) and Schrems II supplementary measures.
References “applicable law” only; no contractual cap or carve-outs. Absence of cap is favourable but may invite negotiation pressure later.
List not included; cannot assess risk.
Entire agreement lacks FM clause; ambiguity on data-protection obligations in such events.
